–––––––\\n4. INTERVIEWER FEEDBACK REQUEST EMAIL\\nSubject: Feedback Request: Interview for {{Role}} with {{CandidateName}}\\n\\nBody:\\nHello {{InterviewerName}},\\n\\nThank you for conducting the interview with {{CandidateName}} for the {{Role}} position on {{InterviewDate}}.\\n\\nPlease provide your feedback (strengths, areas for improvement, recommendation) by replying to this email or via the feedback form: {{FeedbackFormLink}}.\\n\\nWe appreciate your input.\\n\\nBest,  \\n{{YourName}}  \\n{{CompanyName}}\\n\\nSent to: {{InterviewerEmail}}  \\nSent on: {{FeedbackRequestSentDateTime}}\\n\\n––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––\\n5. DECISION EMAIL (OFFER)\\nSubject: Offer for {{Role}} at {{CompanyName}}\\n\\nBody:\\nHello {{CandidateName}},\\n\\nCongratulations! We are pleased to offer you the {{Role}} position at {{CompanyName}}.\\n\\nOffer Details:  \\n- Start Date: {{ProposedStartDate}}  \\n- Compensation: {{Salary}}  \\n- Benefits: {{BenefitsSummary}}\\n\\nPlease review the attached offer letter and let us know if you have any questions. We would appreciate your response by {{OfferExpiryDate}}.\\n\\nWe look forward to having you on our team.\\n\\nSincerely,  \\n{{YourName}}  \\n{{YourTitle}}  \\n{{CompanyName}}  \\nAttachment: Offer_Letter_{{CandidateName}}.pdf\\n\\nSent to: {{CandidateEmail}}  \\nSent on: {{OfferSentDateTime}}\\n\\n––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––\\n6. DECISION EMAIL (REJECTION)\\nSubject: Update on Your Application for {{Role}}\\n\\nBody:\\nHello {{CandidateName}},\\n\\nThank you for interviewing for the {{Role}} position at {{CompanyName}}. We appreciate the time you invested in the process.\\n\\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate. We were impressed by your qualifications and encourage you to apply for future openings.\\n\\nWe wish you every success in your job search and career.\\n\\nBest regards,  \\n{{YourName}}  \